# @name Widget API
# Widget endpoints

### Get all widgets
GET {{baseUrl}}/host/widgets
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### Get widget by ID
@widgetId = your-widget-id-here
GET {{baseUrl}}/host/widgets/{{widgetId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### Create widget
POST {{baseUrl}}/host/widgets
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "adminTitle": "Hero Widget",
  "slug": "hero-widget",
  "variant": "default"
}

### Update widget
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/host/widgets/{{widgetId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "variant": "full-width"
}

### Delete widget
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/host/widgets/{{widgetId}}
